title: NFL Week 17 recap
itunes:title: NFL Week 17 recap
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler -- recap the final week of the 2014 regular season, breaking down all 16 games from Sunday. Plus, Chris Wesseling calls in for the Aaron Rodgers vs. J.J. Watt MVP debate.
